ian information and communications technology company providing end to end ict solutions including telecom services data center services cloud  managed services transformation integration services and application integration services sify technologies limited played an important role during the early spread of internet and ecommerce in india it is listed on nasdaq as sify since  historyedit in november  sify paid ₹ crore for a  stake in indiaworld communications later it acquired the remaining shares for ₹ crore on  june  in  sify sponsored the india olympics team in march  sify made an agreement with makemytrip to run sifys travel portal in january  sify announced prizes for most emails sent under a week contest called sify greenmail promoting emails as an ecofriendly way of communication sify used to run the iway chain of internet service providerinternet cafes in  sify introduced wireless last mile connections with speeds up to  kbps by august  it had over  iway cyber cafes in india in december  sify launched videoconferencing facilities in its internet cafes in  sify with level up games launched a mmorpg in june  the supreme court of india set a legal precedent regarding domain names in the satyam infoway ltd v sifynet solutions pvt ltd lawsuit in november  satyam sold its remaining  shares in sify to infinity capital ventures which is owned by raju vegesna for us million referencesedit  a b anurag k agarwal  business and intellectual property protect your ideas random house india pp – isbn  retrieved  july    a b c d e f sify technologies ltd ads wall street journal retrieved  july    sify takes indiaworld with revised settlement the hindu business line  july  retrieved  july    satyam sponsors olympic team tribune india  august  retrieved  july    makemytrip allies with coke maruti sify  travel portal targets  growth the hindu business line  march  retrieved  july    help plant more trees through ‘sify greenmail’ tribune india  january  retrieved  july    new 